Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要招待各位貴賓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好吃的料理 飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有表演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌 跳舞和變魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 燈裏你會這麼多東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我以為藍華你會的說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危機了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 在AQUA的日曆上 今天開始就是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們領航員也換上了冬裝制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亞利亞社長…你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從早到晚都非常舒適宜人的這幾個月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為秋天的觀光季節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上那個節日的到來 城中的人會開始變多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟要通過啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邊如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:05.10,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 邂逅的結晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了啊 比平時更呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 前輩今天好像沒什麼精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實…小愛一直都沒回我電郵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 她好像跟你說她奶奶身體不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她不是說要來參加Redentore的慶典嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}Redentore：每年7月的第三個星期六舉行的慶典 Redentore\N意為「救世主耶穌基督」 慶典當日會從Zattere築起船橋通往\NGiudecca的Redentore教會供人們前往參拜 晚上則舉行煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說是想看我的新鳳尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是她學業太忙碌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天大概就會回我電郵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一周就到Redentore了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩們今年打算怎麼過Redentore呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋每年都會開公司派對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我可能會跟晃前輩在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年接到艾莉西亞前輩的熟客的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年小愛要是能來的話 我打算跟她一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 話說小後輩去年是怎麼過的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡過的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明過節的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為Redentore不是徹夜狂歡的節日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第二天還要去上學的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 今年的話第二天是休息日 所以沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前輩跟雅典娜前輩也在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有種不好的預感…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…三大精靈為何會聚在一起呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 又是特訓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特訓嗎 嗯 也可以這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 燈裏 我要提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Redentore是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…Redentore就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的威尼斯城的貴族之間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率先展開的夏日慶典…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家坐在各種各樣的船上 一起玩樂到天亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後慢慢地演變成了新威尼斯初秋的風景詩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點結巴 不過勉強算合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…莫非今年是我們六個人一起過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏你們三個負責招待客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,負責招待客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了準備飯菜和飲料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要負責內部裝飾和活動的時間表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很值得一試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次能招待很多客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是大顯身手的好機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳統料理的調味 還有配合飯菜口味的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很煩惱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實啊 我們特別為你們三個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了Redentore專用的大船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是修行啊 修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 真是傷腦筋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我們三個人真的能安排好一艘大船嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好早啊 小後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放學後直接過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因為想盡快給兩位前輩看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:31.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天午休的時候我試著做了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我們大船的邀請函？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 愛麗絲 這個很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你其實很期待Redentore的修行嗎 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然如此 就要好好地幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會加油的 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會超級加油的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會輸的～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把飯菜和飲料放到最後去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先決定要邀請誰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大船的搭載人數 加上我們一共能乘12人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還能請9個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩 晃前輩和雅典娜前輩不能漏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,郵遞員大叔 曉先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 燈裏 你要好好想想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你好像很多朋友的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那藍華想請誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯之類的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們明天就把邀請函發出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能再請一個 找誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…我想請小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級贊成的說 但是來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊 離Redentore只有一周了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她說絕對要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想等她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 那我再給她發一個邀請函的電郵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到Redentore的話 就是鴨肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題在於怎麼醃製啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 太硬的話老年人會咬不動的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用魚和蔬菜來平衡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母喜不喜歡蘑菇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們都試著做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在試做料理期間 雖然充滿了不安和失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 燈裏！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們所做的一切 都是前所未有地新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓時間飛快地溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了讓我們邀請的客人 能夠享受那歡樂的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們心懷這樣的願景 積極地做著準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的日子非常充實而有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在非常期待節日的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 Redentore的日子到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們興奮期待的真正登場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是…誰都不來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛到最後都沒跟我聯繫呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 郵遞員大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以上船了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我第一名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這次邀請的回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬢子 我們來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亞前輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內部裝飾還算過關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 大家這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個超級像雅典娜的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 上衣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 工作遲遲完成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就應該先跟我說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰啊 在那邊玩新婚夫婦對話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 馬尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 呀 真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我家種的麝香葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都這麼精神實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛還沒來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 差不多該把船划出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛 我還以為你不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你奶奶的身體怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已經好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給你驚喜 所以沒跟你聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我出差順便把她帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但比預定的時間稍晚了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 您是小愛的姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她姐姐的丈夫 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次真是謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我現在馬上要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否請你們幫忙照顧愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 當然歡迎之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就拜託幾位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快點開飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子開始餓了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 擺得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表很是不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 各位客人 今天歡迎來到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…雖然僅僅是一點心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家能夠共同度過這初秋之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們無比地榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為這美好的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這是什麼菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是烤鴨和煮得軟軟的荷蘭豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個泡菜放了好多蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道非常奢華呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 謝謝您的誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤飯團…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢挑戰我的得意料理 膽子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在裏面夾了燒肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛肚子餓了吧 要多吃點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個燒鴨可能不錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}注：日文鸭子（かも）和可能（かも）同音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是很不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 剛才那是用鴨子和可能來玩文字遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老頭子的冷笑話禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 餘興節目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 接下來由我和亞利亞社長一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓掌～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內部裝飾很溫馨 讓大家都放鬆下來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你們三人都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起待很長時間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時大家的對話會暫時中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常自然而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的靜寂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常非常喜歡這樣的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈裏前輩 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停電了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來已經12點了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把時間遺忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真難忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不經意地關掉照明燈 很狡猾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 你們也都過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是祖母的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都這麼高興 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能夠得到邀請 真是謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你們三人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們度過了一個非常開心的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這些人 如果沒有了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定就不會相識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美好邂逅的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好邂逅的…結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了給我們製造了這美麗一瞬的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員的種子們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪花和風的聲音 我們終於相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到燈裏姐姐 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我們一起去尋找AQUA的美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去「希望之丘」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想坐坐水上電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}還有啊 還有啊…我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被浪花送來的溫馨一刻所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這顆星球 或許會永遠地守護著各種各樣的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雪白的溫馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
